detaileddescription.para:
The sub-matrix $1\over hw$ $\small \mbox{\( \left(\begin{array}{cc}
                 m_{00} & m_{01}\\
                 m_{10} & m_{11}
                \end{array}\right) \) }
$ contains the scaling and rotation information, the vector  $ \small
  \left(
    \begin{array}{c}
      m_{02}\\
      m_{12}
    \end{array}
  \right)
$ contains the translational part of the transformation.
